graph LR
    ODH[ODH Model Controller]

    %% External Dependencies (Required)
    ODH -->|extends functionality| KServe[KServe v0.13+<br/>REQUIRED]
    ODH -->|creates routes| OSRoute[OpenShift Route API v1<br/>REQUIRED]
    ODH -->|processes templates| OSTemplate[OpenShift Template API v1<br/>REQUIRED]

    %% External Dependencies (Optional)
    ODH -.->|service mesh| Istio[Istio/Maistra v2.5+<br/>OPTIONAL<br/>Control: MESH_DISABLED]
    ODH -.->|authentication| Authorino[Authorino v0.14+<br/>OPTIONAL]
    ODH -.->|alternative auth| Kuadrant[Kuadrant AuthPolicy v1beta3<br/>OPTIONAL]
    ODH -.->|metrics collection| PrometheusOp[Prometheus Operator v0.68+<br/>OPTIONAL]
    ODH -.->|autoscaling| KEDA[KEDA v2.14+<br/>OPTIONAL]
    ODH -.->|webhook certs| CertManager[cert-manager v1.13+<br/>OPTIONAL]
    ODH -.->|NIM models| NGC[NVIDIA NGC API<br/>OPTIONAL<br/>Control: NIM_STATE]

    %% Internal ODH Dependencies
    ODH -.->|reads config| DSC[DataScienceCluster<br/>Internal ODH]
    ODH -.->|reads init config| DSCI[DSCInitialization<br/>Internal ODH]
    ODH -.->|registers metadata| ModelRegistry[Model Registry<br/>Internal ODH<br/>Control: MODELREGISTRY_STATE]

    %% Integration Points - Inbound
    Dashboard[ODH Dashboard<br/>Internal ODH] -.->|UI management| ODH
    Pipelines[Data Science Pipelines<br/>Internal ODH] -.->|auto-deploy| ODH

    %% Integration Points - Outbound
    ODH -->|creates mesh config| IstioCP[Istio Control Plane<br/>15017/TCP gRPC mTLS]
    ODH -->|coordinates reconciliation| KServeCtrl[KServe Controller]
    ODH -->|API calls| K8sAPI[Kubernetes API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS]

    %% External Services (Runtime)
    ODH -.->|model storage| S3[S3 Storage<br/>External Service]

    %% Styling
    style ODH fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,stroke-width:4px,color:#fff

    %% External Required
    style KServe fill:#e74c3c,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style OSRoute fill:#e74c3c,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style OSTemplate fill:#e74c3c,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px

    %% External Optional
    style Istio fill:#999,stroke:#333,stroke-dasharray: 5 5
    style Authorino fill:#999,stroke:#333,stroke-dasharray: 5 5
    style Kuadrant fill:#999,stroke:#333,stroke-dasharray: 5 5
    style PrometheusOp fill:#999,stroke:#333,stroke-dasharray: 5 5
    style KEDA fill:#999,stroke:#333,stroke-dasharray: 5 5
    style CertManager fill:#999,stroke:#333,stroke-dasharray: 5 5
    style NGC fill:#999,stroke:#333,stroke-dasharray: 5 5

    %% Internal ODH
    style DSC fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333
    style DSCI fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333
    style ModelRegistry fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,stroke-dasharray: 5 5
    style Dashboard fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333
    style Pipelines fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333

    %% Platform
    style K8sAPI fill:#f5a623,stroke:#333
    style IstioCP fill:#f5a623,stroke:#333
    style KServeCtrl fill:#f5a623,stroke:#333

    %% External Services
    style S3 fill:#f39c12,stroke:#333,stroke-dasharray: 5 5
